  <entry>
    <title type="html"><![CDATA[mutt配置]]></title>
    <link href="http://justlooks.github.com/blog/2012/07/03/muttpei-zhi/"/>
    <updated>2012-07-03T05:54:00+00:00</updated>
    <id>http://justlooks.github.com/blog/2012/07/03/muttpei-zhi</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2>1. 首先配置getmail收信  </h2>

<p>安装getmail4</p>

<pre><code>apt-get install getmail4
</code></pre>

<p>在非root用户目录下创建邮箱</p>

<pre><code>mkdir -m 700 ~/Mail/inbox/{,tmp,new,cur}    
</code></pre>

<p>创建配置文件</p>

<pre><code>mkdir -p ~/.getmail;cd ~/.getmail
vi rc-gmail
</code></pre>

<p>添加内容</p>

<figure class='code'><figcaption><span>content of rc-gmail  </span></figcaption>
 <div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
<span class='line-number'>6</span>
<span class='line-number'>7</span>
<span class='line-number'>8</span>
<span class='line-number'>9</span>
<span class='line-number'>10</span>
<span class='line-number'>11</span>
<span class='line-number'>12</span>
<span class='line-number'>13</span>
<span class='line-number'>14</span>
<span class='line-number'>15</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='bash'><span class='line'><span class="o">[</span>options<span class="o">]</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="nv">verbose</span> <span class="o">=</span> 2
</span><span class='line'><span class="nv">read_all</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nb">false</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="nv">message_log</span> <span class="o">=</span> ~/.getmail/log
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="o">[</span>retriever<span class="o">]</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="nb">type</span> <span class="o">=</span> SimplePOP3SSLRetriever
</span><span class='line'><span class="nv">server</span> <span class="o">=</span> pop.gmail.com
</span><span class='line'><span class="nv">username</span> <span class="o">=</span> username@gmail.com
</span><span class='line'><span class="nv">port</span> <span class="o">=</span> 995
</span><span class='line'><span class="nv">password</span> <span class="o">=</span> mypass
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="o">[</span>destination<span class="o">]</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="nb">type</span> <span class="o">=</span> Maildir
</span><span class='line'><span class="nv">path</span> <span class="o">=</span> ~/Mail/inbox/
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>测试能够正常收信后配置完成</p>

<figure class='code'><figcaption><span>test for getmail  </span></figcaption>
 <div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
<span class='line-number'>6</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='bash'><span class='line'><span class="nv">$ </span>getmail -r ./rc-gmail
</span><span class='line'>getmail version 4.24.0
</span><span class='line'>Copyright <span class="o">(</span>C<span class="o">)</span> 1998-2009 Charles Cazabon.  Licensed under the GNU GPL version 2.
</span><span class='line'>SimplePOP3SSLRetriever:username@gmail.com@pop.gmail.com:995:
</span><span class='line'>  msg   1/366 <span class="o">(</span>6551 bytes<span class="o">)</span> from &lt;m-767udykq9AUsm7rk5O7vR8Zd9lLZaWb@bounce.linkedin.com&gt; delivered to Maildir /home/xxx/Mail/inbox/
</span><span class='line'>  msg   2/366 <span class="o">(</span>2267 bytes<span class="o">)</span> from &lt;admin@travian.cc&gt; delivered to Maildir /home/xxx/Mail/inbox/
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>如果需要配置多个帐号的话,那么需要写多个rc文件,一个rc文件对应一个邮箱帐号,运行时,通过-r选项传入多个配置文件</p>

<pre><code>getmail -r rc-gmail -r rc-company
</code></pre>

<p>如果需要每隔10分钟收信一次则可以列入计划任务</p>

<figure class='code'><figcaption><span>content of crontab  </span></figcaption>
 <div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='bash'><span class='line'>*/10 * * * * /usr/bin/getmail -r rc-gmail -r rc-company
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>那么现在所有的邮件都是放到一个目录下的,大杂烩,如何对这些邮件进行分类筛选呢?<br/>
比如现在的需求是需要将@company.com来源的邮件放入Mail中的workmate目录下,<br/>
而将公司行政通知(notify@company.com)放到Mail中的notify目录下</p>

<h2>2. 配置procmail对邮件进行过滤</h2>

<p>安装procmail</p>

<pre><code>apt-get install procmail
</code></pre>

<p>创建配置文件</p>

<pre><code>vi ~/.procmailrc
</code></pre>

<p>添加内容</p>

<figure class='code'><figcaption><span>content of .procmailrc  </span></figcaption>
 <div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
<span class='line-number'>6</span>
<span class='line-number'>7</span>
<span class='line-number'>8</span>
<span class='line-number'>9</span>
<span class='line-number'>10</span>
<span class='line-number'>11</span>
<span class='line-number'>12</span>
<span class='line-number'>13</span>
<span class='line-number'>14</span>
<span class='line-number'>15</span>
<span class='line-number'>16</span>
<span class='line-number'>17</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='bash'><span class='line'><span class="nv">MAILDIR</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="nv">$HOME</span>/Mail
</span><span class='line'><span class="nv">DEFAULT</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="nv">$MAILDIR</span>/inbox
</span><span class='line'><span class="nv">LOGFILE</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="nv">$MAILDIR</span>/.procmaillog
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="nv">NOTIFY</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="nv">$MAILDIR</span>/notify
</span><span class='line'><span class="nv">WORKMATES</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="nv">$MAILDIR</span>/workmates
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>:0:
</span><span class='line'>* ^From.*notify@company<span class="se">\.</span>com
</span><span class='line'><span class="k">${</span><span class="nv">NOTIFY</span><span class="k">}</span>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>:0:
</span><span class='line'>* ^From.*@company<span class="se">\.</span>com
</span><span class='line'><span class="k">${</span><span class="nv">WORKMATES</span><span class="k">}</span>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>:0:
</span><span class='line'><span class="k">${</span><span class="nv">DEFAULT</span><span class="k">}</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>创建对应目录</p>

<pre><code>mkdir -p ~/Mail/{workmates,notify}
</code></pre>

<p>同时需要对getmail对应的配置文件做些修改</p>

<pre><code>[destination]
type = Maildir
path = ~/Mail/inbox/
</code></pre>

<p>改为</p>

<pre><code>[destination]
type = MDA_external
path = /usr/bin/procmail
unixfrom = true
</code></pre>

<p>再运行getmail时就会发现邮件被正确的放到对应的目录下了</p>

<pre><code>$ ls ~/Mail/notify/
msg.0sxB  msg.1sxB  msg.9sxB  msg.AtxB  msg.msxB  msg.psxB  msg.-sxB  msg.wsxB
$ ls ~/Mail/workmates/
msg.2sxB  msg.4sxB  msg.6sxB  msg.8sxB  msg.lsxB  msg.osxB  msg.rsxB  msg._sxB  msg.usxB  msg.xsxB  msg.zsxB
msg.3sxB  msg.5sxB  msg.7sxB  msg.BtxB  msg.nsxB  msg.qsxB  msg.ssxB  msg.tsxB  msg.vsxB  msg.ysxB
</code></pre>

<h2>3. 配置mutt显示管理邮件</h2>

<p>在磁盘上的邮件文件需要有工具能够直观的显示,并且提供方便的管理功能,MUTT可以满足需求,它是个强大的邮件管理系统</p>

<p>安装mutt</p>

<pre><code>apt-get install mutt
</code></pre>

<p>编辑配置文件</p>

<pre><code>cp /etc/Muttrc ~/.muttrc
vi ~/.muttrc
</code></pre>

<p>添加如下内容</p>

<figure class='code'><figcaption><span>content of .muttrc  </span></figcaption>
 <div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
<span class='line-number'>6</span>
<span class='line-number'>7</span>
<span class='line-number'>8</span>
<span class='line-number'>9</span>
<span class='line-number'>10</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='bash'><span class='line'><span class="nb">set </span><span class="nv">folder</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s2">&quot;$HOME/Mail&quot;</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="nb">set </span><span class="nv">mbox_type</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s2">&quot;Maildir&quot;</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="nb">set </span><span class="nv">mbox</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s2">&quot;+inbox&quot;</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="nb">set </span><span class="nv">spoolfile</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s2">&quot;~/Mail/inbox&quot;</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="nb">set </span><span class="nv">postponed</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s2">&quot;+postponed&quot;</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="nb">set </span><span class="nv">record</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s2">&quot;+sent&quot;</span>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="nv">mailboxes</span>  <span class="o">=</span><span class="nv">inbox</span> <span class="o">=</span><span class="nv">workmates</span> <span class="o">=</span>notify
</span><span class='line'><span class="nb">set </span><span class="nv">check_new</span> <span class="o">=</span> yes
</span><span class='line'><span class="nb">set </span><span class="nv">timeout</span> <span class="o">=</span> 600
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>另外需要对.procmailrc文件做些修改,因为默认情况下procmail是把邮件存为mbox格式的,为了直观显示邮件标题,需要改为maildir格式
只需要将对应目录结尾加上&#8217;/&#8217;就可以了</p>

<figure class='code'><figcaption><span>content of .procmailrc  </span></figcaption>
 <div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
<span class='line-number'>6</span>
<span class='line-number'>7</span>
<span class='line-number'>8</span>
<span class='line-number'>9</span>
<span class='line-number'>10</span>
<span class='line-number'>11</span>
<span class='line-number'>12</span>
<span class='line-number'>13</span>
<span class='line-number'>14</span>
<span class='line-number'>15</span>
<span class='line-number'>16</span>
<span class='line-number'>17</span>
<span class='line-number'>18</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='bash'><span class='line'><span class="nv">MAILDIR</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="nv">$HOME</span>/Mail
</span><span class='line'><span class="nv">DEFAULT</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="nv">$MAILDIR</span>/inbox
</span><span class='line'><span class="nv">LOGFILE</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="nv">$MAILDIR</span>/.procmaillog
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="nv">NOTIFY</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="nv">$MAILDIR</span>/notify/
</span><span class='line'><span class="nv">WORKMATES</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="nv">$MAILDIR</span>/workmates/
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>:0:
</span><span class='line'>* ^From.*notify@company<span class="se">\.</span>com
</span><span class='line'><span class="k">${</span><span class="nv">NOTIFY</span><span class="k">}</span>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>:0:
</span><span class='line'>* ^From.*@company<span class="se">\.</span>com
</span><span class='line'><span class="k">${</span><span class="nv">WORKMATES</span><span class="k">}</span>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>:0:
</span><span class='line'><span class="k">${</span><span class="nv">DEFAULT</span><span class="k">}</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<h2>4. 关于发送邮件</h2>

<p>安装msmtp</p>

<pre><code>apt-get install msmtp
</code></pre>

<p>编辑配置文件</p>

<pre><code>vi ~/.msmtprc
</code></pre>

<figure class='code'><figcaption><span>content of .msmtprc  </span></figcaption>
 <div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
<span class='line-number'>6</span>
